---
title: Cannellini Bean & Veggie Korma with Garlic Rice & Pickled Cucumber Salsa
description: This protein-packed, flavourful and scrumptious plant-based dish won't just satisfy korma cravings but, with a helping of
aromatic rice to go with it, it'll also satisfy a hungry stomach too!
